#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:2 0a98b30a4e3b412da129ca348cb4c1b2
msgid "蓝牙"
msgstr "Bluetooth"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:17 ba3b7fa9e0b14dd0b5801a8ab5fe4813
msgid "WB2系列支持Bluetooth®LE 5.0 吗？"
msgstr "Does the WB2 series support Bluetooth® LE 5.0?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:18 06d209f50f784f589440f8bd5c28af5f
msgid "支持部分BLE 5.0功能，例如Channel Selection #2，Limited High Duty Cycle Non Connectable Adv， 不支持LE Advertising Extension， 2M PHY，Long Range"
msgstr "Some BLE 5.0 features are supported, such as Channel Selection #2 and Limited High Duty Cycle Non Connectable Adv. LE Advertising Extension, 2M PHY, and Long Range are not supported."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:24 d25ef49f2e094a61a266a9888b005f9b
msgid "可以。蓝牙OTA协议为博流自研，支持断点续传，单次写flash大小可配置。"
msgstr "Yes. The Bluetooth OTA protocol is developed by Bouffalo Lab. It supports breakpoint resume, and the flash write size per operation is configurable."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:28 0771f0782ad847f2aad47f0079269755
msgid "WB2系列的Bluetooth®LE 吞吐量是多少？"
msgstr "What is the Bluetooth® LE throughput of the WB2 series?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:29 71f01f012b8c4e488895af6e388cf1f3
msgid "两个模组之间进行吞吐量测试，BLE连接间隔设置为25ms，实测平均速率为570kbps 模组与手机（mate30 pro）之间进行吞吐量测试，手机app使用BLE调试助手，BLE连接间隔设置为25ms，实测平均速率为400kbps"
msgstr "In a throughput test between two modules, with the BLE connection interval set to 25 ms, the measured average rate was 570 kbps. In a throughput test between the module and a mobile phone (Mate30 Pro), using the BLE Debug Assistant app on the phone and with the BLE connection interval set to 25 ms, the measured average rate was 400 kbps."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:33 214c51d0ec4648f7b6832738f5cd425e
msgid "WB2系列的发射功率是多少？"
msgstr "What is the transmit power of the WB2 series?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:34 71b3a256d803464b91c09b066ffbd1ca
msgid "支持0到15dBm"
msgstr "0 to 15 dBm is supported."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:37 e858e6b23cb8410f935e33449675ff44
msgid "WB2系列支持多少个客户端连接？"
msgstr "How many client connections does the WB2 series support?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:38 0293131f40f1408e8fbf8cfdf4e9e66a
msgid "最大可支持10个蓝牙连接，不局限于蓝牙设备类型（master或slave）。"
msgstr "Up to 10 Bluetooth connections are supported, regardless of Bluetooth device type (master or slave)."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:41 31a1fa5f5277495ca216bfa54103ace8
msgid "Ai-WB2-12F模块可以连接手机放音乐吗"
msgstr "Can the Ai-WB2-12F module connect to a phone to play music?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:42 d564d632082243d19d963d49a6e1844b
msgid "不可以，因为使用的蓝牙是BLE蓝牙，无法传输音频数据。"
msgstr "No. The module uses BLE Bluetooth, which cannot transmit audio data."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:45 b1f57aea74724d73921cb04023e1af21
msgid "为什么我写的ble组件，无法正常工作？"
msgstr "Why does the BLE component I wrote fail to work properly?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:46 c659926b4e58412392b9e24efce15455
msgid "经仔细检查，发现初始化遗漏了bl_sys_init"
msgstr "After careful checking, it was found that bl_sys_init was missing during initialization."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:49 ecb069b59d4f436c87ce7791c49a22bc
msgid "蓝牙4.0的手机能连上WB2系列模组吗"
msgstr "Can a Bluetooth 4.0 phone connect to a WB2 series module?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:50 2b4a98c380634ba9987b95c4a5e5eaa7
msgid "可以，手机端安装BLE蓝牙调试APP即可连接"
msgstr "Yes. Install a BLE Bluetooth debugging app on the phone to connect."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:53 c82d8ab833f84c77b0b43c180d9ec700
msgid "请问一下Ai-WB2-12F模组的蓝牙是只能用来配网的吗？是否可以蓝牙控制？"
msgstr "Is the Bluetooth function of the Ai-WB2-12F module only used for network provisioning? Can it be used for Bluetooth control?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:54 a59ec0f60d604873b97d8791beabbc8c
msgid "该模组的蓝牙可与手机APP中的蓝牙实现数据透传；"
msgstr "The Bluetooth function of this module can implement data transparent transmission with Bluetooth in a mobile app."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:57 6ee4a1622fe44e78bb58693374f64767
msgid "请问Ai-WB2-12F-Kit配置蓝牙之后重启是否会保存配置项"
msgstr "Will the Ai-WB2-12F-Kit save configuration items after Bluetooth is configured and the device is restarted?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:58 ec2c3065204a460abfcd19a460794022
msgid "不会，每次重启需重新配置"
msgstr "No. It needs to be reconfigured after each restart."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:61 af034071e5fd409d903b3fc2247afe97
msgid "WB2系列模块支持蓝牙A2DP功能吗"
msgstr "Does the WB2 series module support Bluetooth A2DP?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:62 9bcd3d63640c4d38aafa5fef4908b72d
msgid "该功能为经典蓝牙功能，目前模块使用为BLE蓝牙，不支持蓝牙A2DP"
msgstr "This is a Classic Bluetooth feature. The current module uses BLE Bluetooth and does not support Bluetooth A2DP."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:65 fd1c59fde02340cd8e78f8fc6f7f038f
msgid "WB2系列模块可以修改蓝牙MAC地址吗"
msgstr "Can the Bluetooth MAC address of the WB2 series module be modified?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:66 ce3c7b769b204f6f9bcc2cd276477360
msgid "可以修改，AT指令和二次开发有相关的教程"
msgstr "Yes. Related tutorials are available for both AT commands and secondary development."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:69 8067a664a0be4b45b4fe9468d820f097
msgid "请问为何Ai-WB2-12F模组实现蓝牙配网功能老是出现重启的现象呢？"
msgstr "Why does the Ai-WB2-12F module keep restarting when implementing Bluetooth network provisioning?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:70 cd9782d5f7704bc59aaeb9601401f3da
msgid "检查一下模组供电情况，供电不足将导致模组重启；"
msgstr "Check the module power supply. Insufficient power supply will cause the module to restart."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:73 d56d3a27143648f5bc8fbe39280e54f1
msgid "WB2-12F蓝牙可以关闭吗"
msgstr "Can Bluetooth on the WB2-12F be turned off?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:74 9db6711899bb43a388318d5f351263ed
msgid "默认蓝牙功能处于关闭状态"
msgstr "The Bluetooth function is disabled by default."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:77 94f8767ac4474b85b1a1c24491c11ca4
msgid "请问WB2-12F模组蓝牙支持2M速率传输么？"
msgstr "Does the WB2-12F module support 2M Bluetooth rate transmission?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:78 e78afc851918462d97a878d134b9a153
msgid "不支持；"
msgstr "No."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:81 cd0fccd3e64b4a49b2f11f472a74b7db
msgid "请问WB2-32S模组可以通过蓝牙获取手机APP的歌词么？"
msgstr "Can the WB2-32S module obtain lyrics from a mobile app via Bluetooth?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:82 f77d5a834fca44dc8416dca9575d51f1
msgid "不支持。"
msgstr "No."

